Package main.project.svm.features

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AvgLineLength
    The average script line length.
    AvgStringLength
    The average length of the strings used in the script.
    DecodingRoutineNum
    The number of code segments that resemble decoding routines, meaning loops that use "long" strings (40+ characters).
    DomModFuncNum
    The number of DOM modifying functions
    EvalNum
    The number of calls to eval() function.
    EventAttachNum
    The number of event attachments.
    HexCharNum
    The number of chars in hex.
    IFrameStringNum
    The number of strings containing "iframe".
    KeywordWordRatio
    The ratio between JS keywords and words in script.
    LongStringNum
    The number of long strings (>40).
    MaxStringEntropy
    The maximum entropy of all the script’s strings.
    MaxStringLength
    The maximum length of the script’s strings.
    PrsIntFrmChrcodeNum
    The number of calls to parseInt and fromCharCode functions
    ScriptEntropy
    The entropy of the script as a whole.
    ScriptLength
    The length of the script in characters.
    SetTimeoutNum
    The number of calls to SetTimeout function
    ShellcodeProbability
    The probability of the script to contain ShellCode.
    StringAssignNum
    Number of direct string assignments.
    StringEntropy
    The entropy of the strings declared in the script.
    StringModFuncNum
    The number of calls to string modification functions.
    SuspiciousObjNum
    The number of suspicious objects.
    SuspiciousStringNum
    The number of Strings containing suspicious words.
    SuspiciousTagNum
    The number of suspicious tag strings (This feature counts the appearance of: 'script', 'object', 'embed', and 'frame' inside JavaScript strings).
    UnescEscNum
    The number of calls to 'escape' and 'unescape'.
    WhitespacePercentage
    The script’s whitespace percentage.
